<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">ف س د:</span> <span class="c2">(فَسَدَ)</span> الشَّيْءُ يَفْسُدُ بِالضَّمِّ <span class="c2">(فَسَادًا)</span> فَهُوَ <span class="c2">(فَاسِدٌ)</span> . وَ <span class="c2">(فَسُدَ)</span> بِالضَّمِّ أَيْضًا <span class="c2">(فَسَادًا)</span> فَهُوَ <span class="c2">(فَسِيدٌ)</span> وَ <span class="c2">(أَفْسَدَهُ فَفَسَدَ)</span> وَلَا تَقُلْ: انْفَسَدَ. وَ <span class="c2">(الْمَفْسَدَةُ)</span> ضِدُّ الْمَصْلَحَةِ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>